com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner

Class DefaultSingleCalculationMarketData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner.DefaultSingleCalculationMarketData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SingleCalculationMarketData

    public final class DefaultSingleCalculationMarketData
extends Object
implements SingleCalculationMarketData
    The default implementation of SingleCalculationMarketData.

    This wraps an instance of CalculationMarketData which contains market data for multiple scenarios. This object returns market data from one of those scenarios. The scenario used as the source of the data is controlled by the scenarioIndex argument.
